content.problem_latex:
Let \[f(x) =
\begin{cases}
x^2+2 &\text{if } x<n, \\
2x+5 &\text{if }x\ge{n}.
\end{cases}
\]If the graph $y=f(x)$ is continuous, find the sum of all possible values of $n$.

